HEADWORD: Reviewer
<hw>Re*view"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who reviews or
reexamines; an inspector; one who examines publications critically, and
publishes his opinion upon their merits; a professional critic of
books.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

